originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: El camino dorado
description: El cuartel general de la resistencia es irrumpido y Lloyd lucha por no ser capturado. Mientras tanto, los Ninjas son capturados por Heavy-Metal, pero encuentran un aliado improbable.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Family BBQ
description: Mordecai wants to get a handshake from Margaret's dad.

title: Ghostfreaked Out
description: Ben's internal demons get externalized when Ghostfreak escapes from his watch and becomes a full fledged being on his own. The renegade alien then realizes he needs to meld with Ben's DNA in order to survive.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: El Silbon
description: Víctor arma un laberinto de maíz embrujado, pero los chicos del pueblo creen que es muy malo. Vic decide hacer que el laberinto sea más aterrador con la ayuda de El Silbón para asustar de verdad a los chicos, pero El Silbón tiene sus propios planes.

title: Adrenalandia Junior
description: El equipo de Tennyson visita la versión segura de Adrenalandia, conocida como "Adrenalandia Jr", y allí terminan enfrentándose a un Kevin 11 amargado y decidido a destruir la diversión segura de todos los demás.

title: The Oct-Father
description: When Princess Morbucks steals Octi, Bubbles' reaction surprises everyone, even her sisters.

title: You Can't Handle the Tooth
description: Uncle Grandpa and Mr. Gus must rescue Pizza Steve from the Tooth Fairy.

title: Tutores Bakugan
description: Dan y Wynton conocen a un extraño chico que los lleva a un laberinto subterráneo, donde descubren que el Bakugan del chico ha sido esclavizado.

title: Conejo culpable
description: Chef intenta conservar su cordura cuando los niños culpan repetidamente a un conejo de peluche llamado Saltarín de todo lo que ellos han hecho.

title: Como construir un dragon
description: Mientras Lloyd y los rebeldes celebran su exitoso golpe contra el Emperador Garmadon, en el Reino de Oni y Dragón, los Ninjas se aventuran con un elaborado escape de las garras del Barón de Hierro y sus Cazadores de Dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Que Rima Con Omnitrix?
description: En un recital de lectura de poesía, Charmcaster lee poemas de Kevin y les causa problemas mágicos a Ben y Gwen cuando produce intercambios mentales que dejan a todos confundidos acerca de quién pelea contra quién.

title: Wild Wild Wheel Part 2
description: WildWheel finds Optimus Prime rebuilding a small Cybertronian town, only to discover the Prime does not recognize him.

title: The Real Orangins!
description: Robin tries again to tell the real origin story of the Teen Titans.

title: La historia de nunca Gwenminar
description: Cuando Chef pierde la última página del libro de cuentos, Gwen se hace cargo y  crea un monstruo en el que todos los chicos comienzan a creer.

title: Cat-Pocalypse
description: When Vic gets sick and is stuck in his room, he spies on Pineapple and becomes convinced that Pineapple is creating an army of zombie cats. Val agrees and the two become obsessed with stopping Pineapple before it's too late!

title: The Crossroads Part 2
description: Optimus and the Autobots team up with some very familiar faces to escape Unspace.

title: Una necesidad inquietante
description: La aparición de un nuevo campo Bakugan hace que los chicos del pueblo corran a buscar a sus propios Bakugan. Pero cuando el campo es contaminado, Lia debe salvarlos a todos.

title: Parents Day
description: It's Parents' Day at Lakewood Plaza Turbo!

title: The Routine
description: Mom and the kids depart for their hard day's work, leaving a seemingly lazy Dad half-asleep on the sofa. Mom has given him one very simple job: buy mayonnaise. However, Dad manages to turn this mundane task into an epic quest, showing that his daily routine isn't as inactive as his family imagine.

title: Demon Prom
description: Trigon makes Raven attend her prom and she brings along the other Titans to upset him.

title: The Outside
description: The family goes to visit Richard's Dad. Based on his basic living standards and extended absence from Richard's life, they assume Frankie must have done a stretch in the slammer. When Frankie comes to stay with the Wattersons, they decide the way to make him comfortable is to make him uncomfortable and turn their house into a prison.

title: Major Competition/Mr. Mojo's Rising
description: Major Competition: There's a new man in town, Major Man, a perfect superhero, who cuts in on the girls' turf. But the girls prove that even though they're minors, they're still the major part of saving the day./Mr. Mojo's Rising: Mojo kidnaps the Professor and forces him to give him the same superpowers at the girls. But once empowered, the true evolution of this supervillain chimp comes to light.

title: Barehanded
description: When Green Lantern leaves his ring in an intergalactic restroom after washing his hands, he discovers it's gone, leading him on a wild chase for the aliens who might have taken it.

title: Countdown
description: Axel has to clean up the living room in time for his uncle's dinner party, but trying to do too much at once leaves him stuck as a toy with Orangutank on the loose and less than an hour until the guests arrive.

title: Agent of Destruction
description: DeBizz helps the Warriors become more famous as their agent, but Vambre returns to adventuring while Prohyas gets caught up in the DeBizz fame trap.

title: Stop the Presses
description: Richard's newspapers aren't selling, so his friends pull out all the stops to put the printed word back on top.

title: Ghost Town Part 2
description: Teletraan-X attempts to rehabilitate Starscream while Optimus, Bee, Hot Rod and Cheetor's quest to save Windblade uncovers a city that is more than meets the eye.

title: Mi Papa Puede Vencer a Tu Papa
description: Cuando un bravucón dice que su papá puede darle una paliza a la mamá de K.O., nuestro héroe acepta con alegría el desafío en nombre de Carol.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Primogenita
description: El Emperador Garmadon ha tomado el control de Ciudad Ninjago donde Lloyd se retira hacia las sombras. Mientras tanto, los otros Ninjas y Wu Joven quedan varados en el Reino de Oni y Dragón y descubren que no están solos.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Hide and Secrets
description: Desperate for answers about Namagem, Mega Man decides to break into his father's lab, which leaves Suna exposed to the vengeful robot.

title: Party Animal
description: Green Arrow, who is determined to finally throw a successful holiday party for the Justice League, finds his plans thwarted when Plastic Man brings a tranquilized super villain to the gathering.

title: Radio Free NinjaGo
description: Lloyd must find his voice as he leads a small resistance to capture the airwaves in Ninjago City. Meanwhile in the First Realm, Iron Baron takes the Ninja on a dragon hunt.

title: Mision Gar
description: El Sr. Gar y KO hacen equipo para una misión secreta.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Thunderhowl Part 2
description: Released after eons of imprisonment, Thunderhowl helps Bee and Chromia navigate the dangerous Crystal City.

title: Drama Bomb
description: The school play goes off the rails when the drama teacher interferes.

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Hoyuelitos
description: Raven compite en un certamen de belleza, creyendo que es la forma de reconectarse con su padre.

title: Bad Heir Day
description: Princess Zange's Autostyle Magisword is stolen and it's up to the Warriors to retrieve it so their royal leader can face her subjects without bad hair.

title: Adrenaland Jr.
description: Team Tennyson visits the safety-neutered version of Adrenaland known as "Adrenaland Jr.", only to end up facing off against a bitter Kevin 11, out to destroy everyone else's good, and safe, time.

title: Panda 2
description: Baby Panda happily lives in a closed off environment for study. But when he's given a new friend, Panda 2, his worldview is shaken, which sets him off on a great adventure.

title: The Best Burger in the World
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to finish their chores before they can have burgers.

title: Breakpoint
description: As Wildvine, Ben goes undercover with an alien crime ring and is tempted by their extreme lifestyle.

title: Me Recuerdas a Alguien
description: Ben y Gwen buscan al tristemente célebre Bojamboo (el Pie Grande del Sur) y descubren que en realidad se trata del Olvideti.

title: Onionless
description: Apple tries to survive a weekend alone while taking care of Onion's plant.

title: Iron & Stone
description: Cole and Young Wu attempt to free their friends, who have been taken captive by a tribe of Dragon Hunters. Meanwhile in Ninjago, Lloyd is reunited with some old friends who may prove valuable allies against Emperor Garmadon.

title: Change the Charge
description: Mega Man tries to stop Elec Man by helping him overcome his destructive habits, but is he being duped in the process?

title: Chad and the Marathon
description: When Chad realizes his lazy habits might be rubbing off on Clarence, he decides to participate in the Aberdale Marathon. However, the athletic Chad doesn't know the first thing about being a runner, and must enlist the help of Clarence to train!

title: Hat Trick
description: When Felix Faust steals Zatanna's magical top hat, the Justice League must help retrieve it before the evil wizard can use it to create a magic portal, releasing the demon Ghast.
